01:21:54,073 --> 01:21:57,074
<i>♪ Nemamo ♪</i>

1044
01:21:57,076 --> 01:21:59,510
<i>♪ manje dana ♪</i>

1045
01:21:59,512 --> 01:22:02,413
<i>♪ da pevamo ♪</i>

1046
