<i>♪ Božije pohvale ♪</i>

1047
01:22:05,451 --> 01:22:08,352
<i>♪ Od kad ♪</i>

1048
01:22:08,354 --> 01:22:11,189
<i>♪ smo prvo ♪</i>

1049
01:22:11,191 --> 01:22:15,095
<i>♪ počeli ♪</i>

1050
01:22:18,231 --> 01:22:21,099
Bart, zamisli šta on vidi gore.

1051
